            "y1": 2275,
            "x2": 1885,
            "y2": 2409
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 10,
        "text": "जानौ । तीनों गुण करि निर्मित मानौ ।। इनको द्रष्टा एक सु",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_13_textline_10.png",
